btrplace.solver.choco

Class DefaultChocoReconfigurationAlgorithmParams

  • java.lang.Object
    • btrplace.solver.choco.DefaultChocoReconfigurationAlgorithmParams
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ChocoReconfigurationAlgorithmParams

    public class DefaultChocoReconfigurationAlgorithmParams
extends Object
implements ChocoReconfigurationAlgorithmParams
    Default implementation of ChocoReconfigurationAlgorithmParams.
    • repair mode is disabled
    • no time limit
    • the transition factory comes from TransitionFactory.newBundle()
    • the view mapper comes from ModelViewMapper.newBundle()
    • the duration evaluator is DurationEvaluators.newBundle()
    • the constraint mapper is ConstraintMapper.newBundle()
    • the Packing constraint is DefaultPacking
    • the Cumulatives view is DefaultCumulatives
    • the AliasedCumulatives view is DefaultAliasedCumulatives
    Author:
    Fabien Hermenier
